    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.15)
    v0 = (v0 - v0)
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.22 + tmp + 0.18) + 0.29) * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.84) * 0.04))
    v0 = (wp.sin(v0) / ((tmp + 0.14 + v0 + 0.32) + (v0 + 0.35 + tmp + 0.79)))
